 />\n蒲崗村道轉落龍翔道個彎位下面嗰度？<br />\n嗰度日頭都冇乜人行<br />\n三十幾年前仲要有命案發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我成日行喎，仲試過幾次凌晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7c78120b07054bf4c725bd6d56a19e6d10ea84","tid":222153,"uid":83836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T10:31:51.000Z","msg":"鑽石山果度真心十年都唔行一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後一次行應該係八歲"},{"pid":"245fd6d8c7d730b55ad71414809e977acc31c20a","tid":222153,"uid":5804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T11:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鑽石山果度真心十年都唔行一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後一次行應該係八歲</blockquote><br />\n鑽石山好陣好顛啊，個隧道有回音架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096e645816df78f88b2c90c51adf8ca2bf3a4e9b","tid":222153,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T11:14:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.iso.cuhk.edu.hk/images/publication/sustainable-campus/201405/original/feature_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.iso.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fimages%2Fpublication%2Fsustainable-campus%2F201405%2Foriginal%2Ffeature_2.jpg&h=a30a7f8a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d06963d332c4c6ba35642747579bafc1f2114ae","tid":222153,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T11:52:53.000Z","msg":"天水圍"},{"pid":"2ba059853e5c5d3f35fdcba4f276a37dc019a225","tid":222153,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T11:53:41.000Z","msg":"More"},{"pid":"2c9a448a836cf6111ff7d0f09483a9f227cbc3e1","tid":222153,"uid":5804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://www.iso.cuhk.edu.hk/images/publication/sustainable-campus/201405/original/feature_2.jpg\" data-thumbna